        attribute it to you and place the same conditions on anything they do with it.)  @ViewBag.SiteName will attribute your caption to you 
        using your @ViewBag.SiteName nickname, or anonymouly if you choose not to use one.
    </li>
    <li>
        If @ViewBag.SiteName suspects you are manipulating the voting system in any way, @ViewBag.SiteName will lock and/or delete your account
        and captions.
    </li>
    <li>
        If @ViewBag.SiteName feels you are a negative influence on the website, @ViewBag.SiteName will lock and/or delete your account and
        captions.
    </li>
    <li>
        In fact, if @ViewBag.SiteName so much as <em>just feels like doing so</em>,
        @ViewBag.SiteName will lock and/or delete your account and captions.  (@ViewBag.SiteName is ruled with an iron fist.)
    </li>
    <li>
        @ViewBag.SiteName is not responsible for you embarrassing yourself on this website or anywhere online.
    </li>
    <li>
        @ViewBag.SiteName is not responsible for someone else embarrassing you on this website or anywhere online.
    </li>
</ul>
